Fran Bow is finally returning home to Aunt Grace after a long and perilous journey. She has escaped the asylum, traversed a land of nightmarish horrors, and made countless strange "friends" along the way. But home might not be all she wished for... find out way new traumas await Fran in the final chapter of Fran Bow!
